reviewText: Bought this as Christmas gift for my son for his collection.
Love it! Some of my favorite cakes are in this season!
My whole family loves the show. We can't get enough of it!
Good seller, fast and accurate, pricing was fair. Great product and condition.
i like to watch cake boss it's one of my favorite shows to watch  customer service was very polite and patient
Loved it as always but why post Season 5 in two volumes?  Besides $$ greed, that is.
